<th style="text-align:center; font-size:1.4em; line-height:1.3em; background:#f4bf92;" colspan="2"><span class="fn summary">Scott Joplin</span></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center;" class="" colspan="2"><a href="/wiki/File:Scott_Joplin_19072.jpg" class="image" title="Scott Joplin 19072.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/ca/Scott_Joplin_19072.jpg" width="220" height="286" border="0" /></a><br /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="text-align:center; line-height:1.5em; background:#f4bf92;" colspan="2">Background information</th>
