<td class="mbox-text" style=""><a href="/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons" title="Wikimedia Commons">Wikimedia Commons</a> has media related to: <b><i><a href="http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Scott_Joplin" class="extiw" title="commons:Category:Scott Joplin">Scott Joplin</a> </i></b></td>
